Source: pg-fact-loader
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.7.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/enova/pg_fact_loader

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-fact-loader
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-fact-loader
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Build fact tables asynchronously with PostgreSQL
 Use queue tables to build and maintain fact tables asynchronously with
 PostgreSQL PGVERSION.
